        "excerpt":"ë¬¸ì œ   https://programmers.co.kr/learn/courses/30/lessons/43238   í’€ì´   def solution(n, times):          left, right = 1, max(times)*n      while left &lt; right:         total = 0         mid = (left+right)//2          for t in times:             total += mid // t          if total &gt;= n:             right = mid         else:             left = mid+1     # print(left, right)          return left   print(solution(2130, [7, 10]))  # ref: https://bit.ly/3pvyFad  ","categories": ["PS"],
